$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
load_message

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
load_message -  This method loads a message for the specified player in the specified folder.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string load_message(string pname,
string fname,
int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pname%^RESET%^ - the players name
%^BOLD%^fname%^RESET%^ - the folder name
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the message number to open
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the text of the message

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/folder_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method loads a message for the specified player in the specified
folder.
.EP

